            <div class="walkthrough-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="inner wrapper">
                <h3>Matching great wines to your occasion. Superfast delivery.</h3>
                <p>Get the same wines as top restaurants delivered on-demand</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="two" class="swiper-slide walkthrough-panel">
            <div class="walkthrough-panel-overlay"></div>
            <div class="inner wrapper">
                <h3>London’s best wines</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Our wines come from the same cellars used by the top restaurants.</li>
                    <li>From producers with the best vineyards in the world.</li>
                    <li>Never settle for supermarket wine again!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="three" class="swiper-slide walkthrough-panel">
